Determine the output of the following code:

```java
public class Calc {
    private int value;

    public Calc(int v) {
        value = v;
    }

    public static int triple(int n) {
        return n * 3;
    }

    public int compute(int n) {
        value += n;
        return triple(value) - n;
    }

    public int getValue() {
        return value;
    }
}

Calc c = new Calc(4);
int result = c.compute(3);
System.out.println(result + " " + c.getValue());
```

