Consider the following class:

```java
public class Counter {
    private int count;

    public Counter() { count = 0; }

    public int increment(int amount) {
        if (amount <= 0) {
            return count;
        }
        count += amount;
        return count;
    }
}
```

The following statements execute in order:

```java
Counter c = new Counter();
System.out.println(c.increment(-5));
System.out.println(c.increment(3));
System.out.println(c.increment(0));
```

What is the output?

