Consider the following class and code segment.

```java
public class Counter
{
    private int count;

    public Counter(int start)
    {
        count = start;
    }

    public void add(int n)
    {
        count += n;
        if (count > 10)
        {
            count = 10;
            return;
        }
        count++;
    }

    public int getCount()
    {
        return count;
    }
}

Counter c = new Counter(8);
c.add(1);
c.add(5);
System.out.println(c.getCount());
```

